{"tid":395499,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小野馬泫雅醉後酥麻撒嬌","createTime":"2017-09-10T23:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T04:58:33.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c9aaffd9d107f1f15922c66773be85cd05a016","tid":395499,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170910/640_29aa40dddd97f7a278dcb96baba97208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170910%2F640_29aa40dddd97f7a278dcb96baba97208.jpg&h=c4b5d66a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泫雅（左）重現喝醉時的撒嬌模樣。翻攝Jtbc<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170910/420_229f07b57fa1262fb4510b91f62f8db3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170910%2F420_229f07b57fa1262fb4510b91f62f8db3.jpg&h=3c1a6ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《認識的哥哥》班底們爭先恐後求泫雅（左二）對自己撒嬌。翻攝Jtbc<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170910/420_b0cdb4b0002c4c90f8dd28cbaa07ed4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170910%2F420_b0cdb4b0002c4c90f8dd28cbaa07ed4b.jpg&h=a6e92866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSuper Junior的希澈（右三）被泫雅捧臉超興奮。翻攝Jtbc<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170910/420_bd3ad77574d89055f8b8202fd252cac8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170910%2F420_bd3ad77574d89055f8b8202fd252cac8.jpg&h=cba7e86e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNU&rsquo;EST的JR（金鐘炫，右三）默默排對讓泫雅撒嬌摸臉。翻攝Jtbc<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170910/420_c3d76ab501a193bd674b98db5cf7938b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170910%2F420_c3d76ab501a193bd674b98db5cf7938b.jpg&h=1e9cc28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泫雅穿上高跟鞋搖呼拉圈。翻攝Jtbc<br />\n<br />\n韓國「性感小野馬」泫雅和「NU&rsquo;EST」JR（金鐘炫）、朴聖光到人氣綜藝節目《認識的哥哥》作客，她的性感魅力讓節目班底希澈、徐章煇等人無不為她傾倒。她穿著學生制服秀出美腿，在節目上一展穿高跟鞋搖呼拉圈的專長，還重現自己喝醉的模樣。金永哲配合著演起狀況劇，對著喝嘴的泫雅說：「妳還好嗎？」只見泫雅嘟嘴嬌喊「人家沒事」，還雙手捧著金永哲的臉，讓希澈激動大喊：「我們也要！」現場男人搶著排隊給女神摸，22歲的JR也默默加入隊伍中，場面十分搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n泫雅最近剛推出新專輯《Following》，主打歌《BABE》在音源榜上成績不俗。泫雅歌曲曲風多走性感路線，秀豐滿上圍及美腿已成家常便飯，而為展現成熟魅力，她在舞台上多穿著高跟鞋熱舞，練就過人的平衡感，還能穿著高跟鞋搖呼拉圈。<br />\n<br />\n她也透露，多數女星在舞台上穿著高跟鞋跳舞時得將鞋子和腳綁起來，以防鞋子掉落，但她完全不需要，不過她強調「私下很少穿高跟鞋」，節目上搖完呼拉圈後，索性躲在講桌後換起平底鞋，平易近人的模樣再次迷倒現場的男性班底及工作人員。（王怡文／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170910/1201067/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170910%2F1201067%2F&d=3xCMysoeWQKAvrXOxL%2FWiZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a283ecd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170910/1201067/</a>"},{"pid":"853b583cb0623fa2dbeabe24d06ec6573d43b4cb","tid":395499,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:56:44.000Z","msg":"淫"},{"pid":"10693cd04b61ce1a5278ae9bcc7b765195586645","tid":395499,"uid":130394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"小野馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大黃蜂呢?"},{"pid":"c8c7f70fc6de127b7c9fb5b0226868f47978af39","tid":395499,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:53:07.000Z","msg":"諗起連詩雅"},{"pid":"9ae7e032bb54d010fa99e55b5fe035620d8b60a3","tid":395499,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"韓國一第淫婦, <br />\n究竟可以頂到幾多秒"},{"pid":"5885a3fb6583a9b83747c6a19eef32b1d852313a","tid":395499,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}